{
  "video_id": "F7k4w5t7D-U",
  "title": "Module 5, V1 - Accounting Policies, Change in Accounting Estimates and Errors - IAS 8",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 2680.0,
      "end_time": 4320.0,
      "text": "Hi, Else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4320.0,
      "end_time": 7880.0,
      "text": "And today we&#39;ll be talking about accounting changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7880.0,
      "end_time": 11270.0,
      "text": "In accounting, we have to deal with an uncertain future."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11270.0,
      "end_time": 13160.0,
      "text": "There are events that need to be included"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13160.0,
      "end_time": 16070.0,
      "text": "in our financial statements now, such as accruals"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 16070.0,
      "end_time": 18260.0,
      "text": "for expenses and liabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 22010.0,
      "text": "However, we don&#39;t know for sure what the amount of the expense"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22010.0,
      "end_time": 23030.0,
      "text": "will be."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23030.0,
      "end_time": 26270.0,
      "text": "Instead, we use an estimate, which is really just an attempt"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26270.0,
      "end_time": 29720.0,
      "text": "to quantify an uncertain future event."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29720.0,
      "end_time": 32210.0,
      "text": "The fact that financial statements include estimates"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32210.0,
      "end_time": 34620.0,
      "text": "leads to three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34620.0,
      "end_time": 40040.0,
      "text": "One, a change may be required to reflect changing circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40040.0,
      "end_time": 43130.0,
      "text": "The circumstances that led to our estimate in the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43130.0,
      "end_time": 46010.0,
      "text": "may now be different, so we have to change our estimate"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46010.0,
      "end_time": 48560.0,
      "text": "to reflect these new circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48560.0,
      "end_time": 52690.0,
      "text": "This is called a change in accounting estimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52690.0,
      "end_time": 55510.0,
      "text": "Two, a change may occur in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55510.0,
      "end_time": 57790.0,
      "text": "due to new accounting policies."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57790.0,
      "end_time": 60220.0,
      "text": "These new policies are chosen because they reflect"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60220.0,
      "end_time": 62680.0,
      "text": "current economic circumstances, meaning"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62680.0,
      "end_time": 66430.0,
      "text": "that the new policy better reflects current reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66430.0,
      "end_time": 69310.0,
      "text": "These changes may be at the discretion of management,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69310.0,
      "end_time": 71860.0,
      "text": "a voluntary change, but they may also"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71860.0,
      "end_time": 75100.0,
      "text": "be an involuntary change due to a change in accounting"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75100.0,
      "end_time": 76480.0,
      "text": "standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76480.0,
      "end_time": 80570.0,
      "text": "This is known as a change in accounting policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80570.0,
      "end_time": 85330.0,
      "text": "Three, a previous estimate may have been an error."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85330.0,
      "end_time": 87640.0,
      "text": "This means that given the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 87640.0,
      "end_time": 90880.0,
      "text": "available at the time the estimate was made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90880.0,
      "end_time": 94570.0,
      "text": "management should have known that it was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94570.0,
      "end_time": 98380.0,
      "text": "Regardless of whether the error is an accident or intentional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98380.0,
      "end_time": 100600.0,
      "text": "maybe to bias a financial statements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100600.0,
      "end_time": 102970.0,
      "text": "makes absolutely no difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102970.0,
      "end_time": 107430.0,
      "text": "This has to be fixed and it is known as an error correction."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107430.0,
      "end_time": 109270.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at each of these individually"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109270.0,
      "end_time": 111610.0,
      "text": "and how they are dealt with."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111610.0,
      "end_time": 114460.0,
      "text": "First is a change in accounting estimate-- also called"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114460.0,
      "end_time": 116230.0,
      "text": "a change in estimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116230.0,
      "end_time": 119230.0,
      "text": "This is where, based on new information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119230.0,
      "end_time": 122080.0,
      "text": "a different estimate is required for the current period"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122080.0,
      "end_time": 125560.0,
      "text": "compared to the estimate that was used in a prior period."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125560.0,
      "end_time": 127630.0,
      "text": "The new estimate may change the carrying value"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127630.0,
      "end_time": 130270.0,
      "text": "of an asset or a liability or it might"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130270.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133870.0,
      "text": "change the way we recognize the use of an asset."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133870.0,
      "end_time": 136510.0,
      "text": "This is always due to what is true today"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136510.0,
      "end_time": 140090.0,
      "text": "or what we expect regarding future benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140090.0,
      "end_time": 143360.0,
      "text": "What are some examples of changes in estimates?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 143360.0,
      "end_time": 147380.0,
      "text": "There are many examples of when we make estimates in accounting"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147380.0,
      "end_time": 149090.0,
      "text": "and any change to these estimates"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149090.0,
      "end_time": 152210.0,
      "text": "would be considered a change in accounting estimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152210.0,
      "end_time": 155660.0,
      "text": "A few examples would be a change to the percentage we"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155660.0,
      "end_time": 158960.0,
      "text": "use to calculate the allowance for doubtful accounts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158960.0,
      "end_time": 160910.0,
      "text": "a change in the value of our investments"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160910.0,
      "end_time": 164090.0,
      "text": "due to new market conditions, a change"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164090.0,
      "end_time": 167150.0,
      "text": "in the estimated useful life of long-lived assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167150.0,
      "end_time": 170370.0,
      "text": "or the residual value, the percentage used"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170370.0,
      "end_time": 173400.0,
      "text": "to calculate warranty provisions may change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173400.0,
      "end_time": 176760.0,
      "text": "and the value of inventory when obsolescence is an issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176760.0,
      "end_time": 178850.0,
      "text": "may also change."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178850.0,
      "end_time": 181340.0,
      "text": "There are many other examples of changes in estimates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 181340.0,
      "end_time": 183890.0,
      "text": "because estimates are a normal part of accounting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183890.0,
      "end_time": 185930.0,
      "text": "particularly accrual accounting, which is"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185930.0,
      "end_time": 189570.0,
      "text": "required by both IFRS and ASPE."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189570.0,
      "end_time": 192750.0,
      "text": "Because a change in estimate is based on new information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 192750.0,
      "end_time": 195540.0,
      "text": "that change does not relate to prior periods"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 195540.0,
      "end_time": 198660.0,
      "text": "after all, when the estimate was made in the prior period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198660.0,
      "end_time": 202440.0,
      "text": "it was the information available then that was important."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202440.0,
      "end_time": 204750.0,
      "text": "As long as the estimate in the prior period"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 204750.0,
      "end_time": 208470.0,
      "text": "was made in good faith using the information available"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 208470.0,
      "end_time": 211320.0,
      "text": "at that time, then it is acceptable"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211320.0,
      "end_time": 213580.0,
      "text": "and should not be changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 213580.0,
      "end_time": 216630.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why a change in estimate does not require any changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 216630.0,
      "end_time": 218400.0,
      "text": "to past financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218400.0,
      "end_time": 221700.0,
      "text": "Instead, a change in estimate is treated as a perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221700.0,
      "end_time": 224280.0,
      "text": "adjustment, meaning the changes implemented"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224280.0,
      "end_time": 226620.0,
      "text": "for the current and future periods."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226620.0,
      "end_time": 229620.0,
      "text": "Past periods are never changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229620.0,
      "end_time": 232620.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it is very difficult to differentiate"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232620.0,
      "end_time": 234780.0,
      "text": "between a change in accounting estimate"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 234780.0,
      "end_time": 237090.0,
      "text": "and a change in accounting policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 237090.0,
      "end_time": 240570.0,
      "text": "For instance, if a business changes its depreciation"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 240570.0,
      "end_time": 243900.0,
      "text": "method, say from straight line to declining balance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 243900.0,
      "end_time": 248940.0,
      "text": "is that a change in estimate or a change in accounting policy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248940.0,
      "end_time": 251310.0,
      "text": "It may be true that it&#39;s a change in estimate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 251310.0,
      "end_time": 254400.0,
      "text": "because prior estimates of how the benefits would flow"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 254400.0,
      "end_time": 256920.0,
      "text": "to the business have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 256920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259529.00000000003,
      "text": "Or is it a change in accounting policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 259529.0,
      "end_time": 262110.0,
      "text": "which will result in more reliable and relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 262110.0,
      "end_time": 265470.0,
      "text": "information with regards to the company&#39;s financial position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 265470.0,
      "end_time": 268210.0,
      "text": "performance, or cash flow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 268210.0,
      "end_time": 271510.0,
      "text": "This requires professional judgment to determine."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 271510.0,
      "end_time": 275290.0,
      "text": "Under IFRS, if it is unclear whether a change is"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275290.0,
      "end_time": 278410.0,
      "text": "one of policy or estimate, the change"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 278410.0,
      "end_time": 282660.0,
      "text": "should be treated as a change in accounting estimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 282660.0,
      "end_time": 284580.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s very important to know with regards"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 284580.0,
      "end_time": 286270.0,
      "text": "to a change in estimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 286270.0,
      "end_time": 290130.0,
      "text": "Remember, a change in estimate requires perspective adjustment"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 290130.0,
      "end_time": 293700.0,
      "text": "with no changes to the prior year&#39;s financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293700.0,
      "end_time": 295590.0,
      "text": "There are also no disclosure requirements"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295590.0,
      "end_time": 297720.0,
      "text": "for a change in estimate as they are a normal part"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 297720.0,
      "end_time": 300410.0,
      "text": "of the accounting process."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 300410.0,
      "end_time": 302500.0,
      "text": "Next is a change in accounting policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 302500.0,
      "end_time": 306850.0,
      "text": "A change in policy can be either voluntary or compulsory."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 306850.0,
      "end_time": 310420.0,
      "text": "If a new policy would provide more reliable and relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 310420.0,
      "end_time": 313300.0,
      "text": "information to the stakeholders with regards to the company&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 313300.0,
      "end_time": 317270.0,
      "text": "financial position, performance, or cash flows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 317270.0,
      "end_time": 320350.0,
      "text": "then it is a voluntary change in accounting policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 320350.0,
      "end_time": 322610.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s at the discretion of management."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 322610.0,
      "end_time": 324520.0,
      "text": "Note those two words--"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 324520.0,
      "end_time": 328030.0,
      "text": "reliable, which references faithful representation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 328030.0,
      "end_time": 329470.0,
      "text": "and relevant."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 329470.0,
      "end_time": 333500.0,
      "text": "These are both fundamental qualitative characteristics."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 333500.0,
      "end_time": 337090.0,
      "text": "These are critical to ensure useful financial information."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 337090.0,
      "end_time": 338740.0,
      "text": "No wonder they are used to justify"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 338740.0,
      "end_time": 341320.0,
      "text": "a change in accounting policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 341320.0,
      "end_time": 343240.0,
      "text": "The new accounting policy must better"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 343240.0,
      "end_time": 345430.0,
      "text": "reflect the economic circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 345430.0,
      "end_time": 349060.0,
      "text": "or the nature of the operations moving forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 349060.0,
      "end_time": 352600.0,
      "text": "The burden is on management to explain to stakeholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 352600.0,
      "end_time": 355480.0,
      "text": "why the new method is more reliable and relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 355480.0,
      "end_time": 358120.0,
      "text": "than the method used in prior years."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 358120.0,
      "end_time": 361360.0,
      "text": "An example of a voluntary change in accounting policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 361360.0,
      "end_time": 362920.0,
      "text": "would be the movement from a FIFO"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 362920.0,
      "end_time": 367360.0,
      "text": "method of valuing inventory to a weighted average method."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 367360.0,
      "end_time": 371320.0,
      "text": "If a new policy is due to new or changed accounting standards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 371320.0,
      "end_time": 374230.0,
      "text": "then it is considered a compulsory change."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 374230.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "For instance, a move from Canadian GAAP to IFRS"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380440.0,
      "text": "was a compulsory change of accounting policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 380440.0,
      "end_time": 384040.0,
      "text": "How do we present a change in accounting policy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 384040.0,
      "end_time": 386770.0,
      "text": "Retrospective application-- sometimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 386770.0,
      "end_time": 389650.0,
      "text": "called retroactive application-- requires"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 389650.0,
      "end_time": 393040.0,
      "text": "that both the current year and all prior years"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 393040.0,
      "end_time": 396160.0,
      "text": "be adjusted to reflect the new policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 396160.0,
      "end_time": 399250.0,
      "text": "After the change, it should look like the company never"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 399250.0,
      "end_time": 402880.0,
      "text": "did anything but the new policy since all prior year&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 402880.0,
      "end_time": 407070.0,
      "text": "financial statements would be updated for the new policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 407070.0,
      "end_time": 410220.0,
      "text": "This is consistent with the enhancing qualitative"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 410220.0,
      "end_time": 413040.0,
      "text": "characteristic of comparability."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 413040.0,
      "end_time": 416310.0,
      "text": "Only by changing all the prior year&#39;s financial statements can"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 416310.0,
      "end_time": 419580.0,
      "text": "the financial statements remain comparable between periods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 419580.0,
      "end_time": 422310.0,
      "text": "allowing for trend analysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 422310.0,
      "end_time": 425310.0,
      "text": "Note that a summary change flowing through equity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 425310.0,
      "end_time": 427740.0,
      "text": "more specifically retained earnings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 427740.0,
      "end_time": 431400.0,
      "text": "is provided for the earliest prior period presented."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 431400.0,
      "end_time": 432880.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 432880.0,
      "end_time": 436710.0,
      "text": "Well, if the financial reports included the current year, say"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 436710.0,
      "end_time": 442680.0,
      "text": "2019, and two prior years, meaning 2018 in 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 442680.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "all three years would be updated for the change."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448860.0,
      "text": "This means that individual account balances"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 448860.0,
      "end_time": 452490.0,
      "text": "would be adjusted as if the new accounting policy had always"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 452490.0,
      "end_time": 454200.0,
      "text": "been in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 454200.0,
      "end_time": 458370.0,
      "text": "In addition, in the equity section of 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 458370.0,
      "end_time": 461010.0,
      "text": "a summary adjustment to retained earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 461010.0,
      "end_time": 464970.0,
      "text": "would show the total impact of the change on all years"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 464970.0,
      "end_time": 468550.0,
      "text": "prior to 2017."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 468550.0,
      "end_time": 472030.0,
      "text": "What if it&#39;s no longer possible to reconstruct all the data"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 472030.0,
      "end_time": 474370.0,
      "text": "for prior years because the details are"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 474370.0,
      "end_time": 476440.0,
      "text": "no longer available?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 476440.0,
      "end_time": 478690.0,
      "text": "Or it might be true that the data is available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 478690.0,
      "end_time": 482710.0,
      "text": "but the cost of obtaining the data would be very high."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 482710.0,
      "end_time": 486250.0,
      "text": "In this case, where it&#39;s impractical to provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 486250.0,
      "end_time": 489850.0,
      "text": "retrospective application, partial retrospective"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 489850.0,
      "end_time": 492130.0,
      "text": "application is allowed."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 492130.0,
      "end_time": 494110.0,
      "text": "In this case, a summary adjustment"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 494110.0,
      "end_time": 497620.0,
      "text": "to retained earnings in the last comparative year where"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 497620.0,
      "end_time": 501730.0,
      "text": "the details can be determined is allowed."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 501730.0,
      "end_time": 505150.0,
      "text": "If it is no longer possible to determine even the impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 505150.0,
      "end_time": 507670.0,
      "text": "on the opening balances of the current year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 507670.0,
      "end_time": 509620.0,
      "text": "then a change in accounting policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 509620.0,
      "end_time": 511990.0,
      "text": "would be applied prospectively."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 511990.0,
      "end_time": 515580.0,
      "text": "The same way a change in accounting estimate is."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 515580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518250.00000000006,
      "text": "The disclosure requirements for a change in accounting policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 518250.0,
      "end_time": 519690.0,
      "text": "are extensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 519690.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521909.00000000006,
      "text": "This allows the stakeholders to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 521909.0,
      "end_time": 524460.0,
      "text": "why the change was made and how it impacts"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 524460.0,
      "end_time": 526910.0,
      "text": "current and prior years."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 526910.0,
      "end_time": 530250.0,
      "text": "Disclosure requirements are as follows."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 530250.0,
      "end_time": 532730.0,
      "text": "If that change is due to a change in standards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 532730.0,
      "end_time": 534470.0,
      "text": "full information about the change"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 534470.0,
      "end_time": 537380.0,
      "text": "and its impact on the financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 537380.0,
      "end_time": 541310.0,
      "text": "If the change is voluntary, what the change was and why"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 541310.0,
      "end_time": 543560.0,
      "text": "the new policy is considered to provide"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 543560.0,
      "end_time": 548010.0,
      "text": "more reliable and relevant information to stakeholders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 548010.0,
      "end_time": 550350.0,
      "text": "the effect of the change on each line item"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 550350.0,
      "end_time": 553990.0,
      "text": "on the statements for current and prior periods."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 553990.0,
      "end_time": 557130.0,
      "text": "If full retrospective application is not possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 557130.0,
      "end_time": 561170.0,
      "text": "why it&#39;s not possible, and how the change will be handled."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 561170.0,
      "end_time": 565190.0,
      "text": "Finally, what the effect on future periods might be."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 565190.0,
      "end_time": 568070.0,
      "text": "This is applicable also to new standards that have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 568070.0,
      "end_time": 570980.0,
      "text": "issued, but not yet adopted."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 570980.0,
      "end_time": 574340.0,
      "text": "This means that a business must disclose reliable information"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 574340.0,
      "end_time": 577700.0,
      "text": "on how future standards might affect the statements going"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 577700.0,
      "end_time": 580070.0,
      "text": "forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 580070.0,
      "end_time": 582200.0,
      "text": "Onward to the correction of an error."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 582200.0,
      "end_time": 584510.0,
      "text": "This is when in a prior period there"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 584510.0,
      "end_time": 589410.0,
      "text": "was a material error, either intentional or accidental."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 589410.0,
      "end_time": 591570.0,
      "text": "Similar to a change in accounting policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 591570.0,
      "end_time": 594480.0,
      "text": "retrospective application requires"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 594480.0,
      "end_time": 598230.0,
      "text": "that both the current year and all prior years be adjusted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 598230.0,
      "end_time": 602670.0,
      "text": "so that it is as if the error never happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 602670.0,
      "end_time": 605370.0,
      "text": "If the error was in one of the prior periods that"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 605370.0,
      "end_time": 607770.0,
      "text": "is provided for comparative purposes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 607770.0,
      "end_time": 611040.0,
      "text": "the error must be corrected and the resulting change"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 611040.0,
      "end_time": 614340.0,
      "text": "flowed through all subsequent years."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 614340.0,
      "end_time": 617930.0,
      "text": "If the error occurred in periods prior to the comparative years"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 617930.0,
      "end_time": 622390.0,
      "text": "shown, then the opening balances of assets, liabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 622390.0,
      "end_time": 626130.0,
      "text": "and equity, including a summary change to retained earnings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 626130.0,
      "end_time": 628460.0,
      "text": "must be presented."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 628460.0,
      "end_time": 630830.0,
      "text": "A correction of an error must be disclosed in the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 630830.0,
      "end_time": 632900.0,
      "text": "to the financial statements, including"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 632900.0,
      "end_time": 636620.0,
      "text": "an explanation of the error, the accounts and amounts changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 636620.0,
      "end_time": 639170.0,
      "text": "in all prior periods, and the amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 639170.0,
      "end_time": 641210.0,
      "text": "of the summary correction to retained earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 641210.0,
      "end_time": 644350.0,
      "text": "in the earliest prior period provided."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 644350.0,
      "end_time": 647860.0,
      "text": "In addition, if full retrospective restatement"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 647860.0,
      "end_time": 651490.0,
      "text": "is not possible because the details are unknown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 651490.0,
      "end_time": 654250.0,
      "text": "an explanation of why it&#39;s not possible to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 654250.0,
      "end_time": 657790.0,
      "text": "the details and how the error was corrected"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 657790.0,
      "end_time": 660020.0,
      "text": "must be included in the note."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 660020.0,
      "end_time": 662210.0,
      "text": "Finally, the affect of the correction"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 662210.0,
      "end_time": 664910.0,
      "text": "on basic and fully diluted earnings per share"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 664910.0,
      "end_time": 668610.0,
      "text": "must be reported for each prior period presented."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 668610.0,
      "end_time": 671320.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it for accounting changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 671320.0,
      "end_time": 673740.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much for joining me."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 673740.0,
      "end_time": 675900.0,
      "text": "In an upcoming video, I&#39;ll be demonstrating"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 675900.0,
      "end_time": 679260.0,
      "text": "one method you can use to solve the change in accounting policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 679260.0,
      "end_time": 682340.0,
      "text": "or the correction of an error."
    }
  ]
}